COLD WALLET / OFFLINE WALLET

1ï¸What is a Cold Wallet?
ğŸ“Œ Definition
A cold wallet is a cryptocurrency wallet that is not connected to the internet and is used to store private keys offline for maximum security.
â¡ï¸ Because it remains offline, it is also called an offline wallet.

2ï¸.Why Cold Wallets are used?
Cold wallets are mainly used for:
	â€¢	Long-term storage of cryptocurrency
	â€¢	Storing large amounts of crypto
	â€¢	Protection from hacking & malware
	â€¢	Institutional and professional use

3ï¸.List of Offline (Cold) Wallets
